{"tid":1526280,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[打機撚注意]不如去信ubisoft 叫佢哋將SDU係 rainbow 6 除名","createTime":"2019-09-01T05:09:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T10:54:26.000Z","uid":95294,"like":119,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"143fe6fddf783465a480371575f383b76f70e233","tid":1526280,"uid":95294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T05:09:47.000Z","msg":"如題<br />\n我諗如果係一個外國都算多人玩嘅遊戲 將呢班所謂嘅「特種部隊」除名<br />\n<br />\n至少應該都會引起唔少外國人關注 或者會對香港發生嘅事感到好奇<br />\n<br />\n最重點係香港SDU根本無資格同其他特種部隊齊名！<br />\n<br />\n所以提出黎希望大家考慮吓呢個方法有無用，雖然唔會對班狗做成咩直接影響，但起碼都算係一個方法引起外國一班未必好睇新聞，表達到班狗係香港社會嘅惡行！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7101b8a755e1bee40dee83b763c7eef462cee722","tid":1526280,"uid":177336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T05:10:38.000Z","msg":"901 機場攻略<br />\n麻煩大家用盡所有方法傳開佢<br />\n<br />\n- <span style=\"color: red;\">準時</span>到機場，唔係一點先出門口<br />\n- 衣着同裝備冇任何限制，最緊要保護自己<br />\n- 集合地點：機場巴士總站(暢達路)<br />\n- 測試方法：排隊戰術，見到<span style=\"color: red;\">有隊就排</span>；利用人數優勢，<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好單獨行事</span><br />\n- 唔好同任何遊客有肢體碰撞<br />\n- 去機場：<span style=\"color: red;\">以巴士為優先</span>，機場快線集中係香港同青衣站上車<br />\n- 已經準備左幾套應變方案，根據現場情況<span style=\"color: red;\">隨時轉變</span>，要密切留意住 901 機場 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=dE5eED8%2BMjLqHtNzOSR2XzsyqOHkMMjDRpVYVMaq87A%3D&h=5c2c19d2\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P5XusdO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP5XusdO.jpg&h=31adcd48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cTXKf68.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcTXKf68.jpg&h=74d57433&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qAxaV7a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqAxaV7a.jpg&h=13c2eb06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/otZAnNa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FotZAnNa.jpg&h=f10fa124&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d88c42524da04fc15cde9354dfba05291e484c5d","tid":1526280,"uid":55493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T05:11:45.000Z","msg":"做得過"},{"pid":"e02b8cf8647267c2d23b868fc171bcb671ecb0e1","tid":1526280,"uid":66639,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T05:15:39.000Z","msg":"叫佢改簡介啦<br />\n「專門扮示威者鬼鬼祟祟」改埋做3速<br />\n技能改埋汽油彈"},{"pid":"fe61f879e591e943c755aeea5a03e0eb6a69f3a7","tid":1526280,"uid":95294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T05:55:37.000Z","msg":"點睇？"},{"pid":"e0568515c7c422ba8003e4cad0a55b655e36e424","tid":1526280,"uid":231522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T05:58:12.000Z","msg":"寫封出黎 自然有人寄<br />\n要所有人知道黑狗"},{"pid":"42e431043ec5d27aa1b9ed5b59d8ca9c29c407d4","tid":1526280,"uid":101433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fe61f879e591e943c755aeea5a03e0eb6a69f3a7","tid":1526280,"uid":95294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T05:55:37.000Z","msg":"點睇？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T05:58:13.000Z","msg":"支持 有無範本copy<br />\n伸利：英文差 有玩R6"},{"pid":"015b709ccd9ce8642a08368806f6a35d7ca9cb15","tid":1526280,"uid":280648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e02b8cf8647267c2d23b868fc171bcb671ecb0e1","tid":1526280,"uid":66639,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T05:15:39.000Z","msg":"叫佢改簡介啦<br />\n「專門扮示威者鬼鬼祟祟」改埋做3速<br />\n技能改埋汽油彈"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T05:58:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img 